data.description:
7575 Shadow Lake Dr, Panama City Beach, FL 32407 is a single family home that contains 1,496 sq ft and was built in 2021. It contains 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. This home last sold for $236,800 in February 2021. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $357,000. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $2,328/mo.
